[WIND BLOWING]

74
00:07:19,960 --> 00:07:21,791
Boys, turn the TV off. James.

75
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:24,190
MARY:
Come on. Everything's getting cold.

76
00:07:25,360 --> 00:07:27,794
ROBIN: Ketchup.
JOHN: Where have you been, honey?

77
00:07:27,960 --> 00:07:29,313
[DOGS GROWL]

