79
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:34,916
Maybe, uh... Maybe next year we'll get
Stephen home, make up the full crew.

80
00:07:35,080 --> 00:07:37,753
- Would you like to see Stephen?
- Yeah, that'd be awesome.

81
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:41,037
